      Our 3-piece blue printed poly crepe fabric suit set features a straight-fit kurta with a notched neckline and three-quarter sleeves. Complemented with trousers with a partially elasticated waistband and roomy pockets, and a dupatta. Adorned with captivating ethnic motifs prints, this style is perfect for elevated everyday wear.

      Accessorise with jhumka earrings, a fold-over clutch bag, and embellished juttis to complete the look.

      The model (height 170 cm) is wearing a size S.
